-- BHP says sees $3.7 billion in synergies with Rio
-- 
-- Sun Nov 11, 2007 10:47pm EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/11/12/us-riotinto-bhpbilliton-deal-idUSSYU00347620071112

 

 SYDNEY  (Reuters) - BHP Billiton Ltd/Plc ( BHP.AX ) ( BLT.L ) said on Monday it sees $3.7 billion in synergies if it succeeds in acquiring rival Rio Tinto Ltd/Plc ( RIO.AX )<RIO.L. 

 BHP also said it planned a $30 billion share buy back if the acquisition goes ahead. ($1=A$1.10)